			Company Description 


			Mercury General Corp. is a holding company, which engages in the provision of insurance services. It operates through the Property & Casualty Lines; and Other. The Property & Casualty Lines offers insurance products on private passengers automobile, commercial properties, and vehicles. The Other seg...
		


                Mercury General Corp. is a holding company, which engages in the provision of insurance services. It operates through the Property & Casualty Lines; and Other. The Property & Casualty Lines offers insurance products on private passengers automobile, commercial properties, and vehicles. The Other segment includes automobile mechanical breakdown warranties sold through dealerships and credit unions. The company was founded by George Joseph in 1961 and is headquartered in Los Angeles, CA.
            




